<h1>Nyhedsgruppen dk.edb.internet.webdesign.serverside.php</h1><p>Gruppen er til spørgsmål/diskussion af de problemer der er ved at fremstille websider ved brug af PHP.</p><hr /><div class='newsbox'><img src='/site/graphics/icons/icon_reply.gif' alt=' | ' />&nbsp;<a href='/nyhedsgrupper/dk_edb_internet_webdesign_serverside_php/default.asp?mode=form&amp;ReplyID=%3Cba0au7%242ilq%241%40news%2Ecybercity%2Edk%3E'>Svar på dette indlæg</a>&nbsp;<img src='/site/graphics/icons/icon_new.gif' alt=' | ' />&nbsp;<a href='/nyhedsgrupper/dk_edb_internet_webdesign_serverside_php/default.asp?mode=form'>Skriv et nyt indlæg</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;<img src='/site/graphics/icons/icon_list.gif' alt=' | ' />&nbsp;<a href='/nyhedsgrupper/dk_edb_internet_webdesign_serverside_php/default.asp'>dk.edb.internet.webdesign.serverside.php</a></div>

<!-- FreeFind End No Index -->

<ul class='messageheaderlist'><li class='messageheaderlist'><strong class='diff'><span class='messageheader'>Afsender:</span></strong> tonny&nbsp;jørgensen&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href='mailto:hest@aub.dk'><img src='/site/graphics/icons/icon.newsgroups.mail.gif' alt='hest@aub.dk' /></a></li><li class='messageheaderlist'><strong class='diff'><span class='messageheader'>Organisation:</span></strong> Cybercity</li><li class='messageheaderlist'><strong class='diff'><span class='messageheader'>Dato:</span></strong> 15. maj 2003 kl. 17:12</li><li class='messageheaderlist'><strong class='diff'><span class='messageheader'>Emne:</span></strong> <strong>problem med mail()</strong></li></ul>

<p><span class='normal'>jeg har lavet en formular p&#229; en hjemmeside der sender variable videre til et </span><br /><span class='normal'>php mailscript via $HTTP_POST </span><br /><span class='normal'> </span><br /><span class='normal'>formen ser s&#229;ledes ud </span><br /><span class='normal'> </span><br /><span class='normal'>&lt;form action=&quot;mail.php&quot; method=&quot;post&quot;> </span><br /><span class='normal'>&lt;table> </span><br /><span class='normal'>&lt;tr>&lt;td class=&quot;form&quot;>&lt;a>&lt;b>Navn: &lt;/b>&lt;/a>&lt;/td>&lt;td class=&quot;form&quot;>&lt;input </span><br /><span class='normal'>type=&quot;text&quot; name=&quot;navn&quot;>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr> </span><br /><span class='normal'>&lt;tr>&lt;td class=&quot;form&quot;>&lt;a>&lt;b>Kontaktinfo - tlf eller email: &lt;/b>&lt;/a>&lt;/td>&lt;td </span><br /><span class='normal'>class=&quot;form&quot;>&lt;input type=&quot;text&quot; name=&quot;info&quot;>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr> </span><br /><span class='normal'>&lt;tr>&lt;td class=&quot;form&quot; valign=&quot;top&quot;>&lt;a>&lt;b>Tr&#230;ffetidspunkt: &lt;/b>&lt;/a>&lt;/td>&lt;td </span><br /><span class='normal'>class=&quot;form&quot;>&lt;input type=&quot;text&quot; name=&quot;tidspunkt&quot;>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr> </span><br /><span class='normal'>&lt;tr>&lt;td class=&quot;form&quot; valign=&quot;top&quot;>&lt;a>&lt;b>Bem&#230;rkninger: &lt;/b>&lt;/a>&lt;/td>&lt;td </span><br /><span class='normal'>class=&quot;form&quot;>&lt;textarea name=&quot;text&quot; rows=&quot;10&quot; cols=&quot;20&quot;>&lt;/textarea>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr> </span><br /><span class='normal'>&lt;tr>&lt;td colspan=&quot;2&quot; class=&quot;form&quot;>&lt;input type=&quot;submit&quot; value=&quot;send </span><br /><span class='normal'>besked&quot;>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr> </span><br /><span class='normal'>&lt;/table> </span><br /><span class='normal'>&lt;/form> </span><br /><span class='normal'> </span><br /><span class='normal'>og mail.php ser s&#229;ledes ud </span><br /><span class='normal'> </span><br /><span class='normal'>&lt;? </span><br /><span class='normal'> </span><br /><span class='normal'>// mail thingy </span><br /><span class='normal'> </span><br /><span class='normal'>/* recipients */ </span><br /><span class='normal'>$to  = &quot;&lt;<a href='http://hest@aub.dk'>hest@aub.dk</a>>&quot;; </span><br /><span class='normal'> </span><br /><span class='normal'> </span><br /><span class='normal'>/* subject */ </span><br /><span class='normal'>$subject = &quot;henvendelse fra hjemmesiden&quot;; </span><br /><span class='normal'> </span><br /><span class='normal'>/* message */ </span><br /><span class='normal'>$message = $navn . ' skrev: &lt;br> ' . $text . '&lt;br>kontaktinfo:' . $info . </span><br /><span class='normal'>'&lt;br>&lt;br>&lt;b>tr&#230;ffes bedst: ' . $tidspunkt . '&lt;/b>'; </span><br /><span class='normal'> </span><br /><span class='normal'> </span><br /><span class='normal'> </span><br /><span class='normal'> </span><br /><span class='normal'>/* To send HTML mail, you can set the Content-type header. */ </span><br /><span class='normal'>$headers  = &quot;MIME-Version: 1.0\r\n&quot;; </span><br /><span class='normal'>$headers .= &quot;Content-type: text/html; charset=iso-8859-1\r\n&quot;; </span><br /><span class='normal'> </span><br /><span class='normal'>/* additional headers */ </span><br /><span class='normal'>$headers .= &quot;From: webmaster\r\n&quot;; </span><br /><span class='normal'> </span><br /><span class='normal'> </span><br /><span class='normal'>/* and now mail it */ </span><br /><span class='normal'>mail($to, $subject, $message,$headers); </span><br /><span class='normal'> </span><br /><span class='normal'>header(&quot;Location: <a href='http://www.fordijegkan.dk?page=sendt&quot;);'>http://www.fordijegkan.dk?page=sendt&quot;);</a> </span><br /><span class='normal'> </span><br /><span class='normal'>?> </span><br /><span class='normal'> </span><br /><span class='normal'>formularen kan afpr&#248;ves p&#229; </span><br /><span class='normal'><a href='http://www.fordijegkan.dk/index.php?contact=dummy&amp;page=dummy'>http://www.fordijegkan.dk/index.php?contact=dummy&amp;page=dummy</a> </span><br /><span class='normal'> </span><br /><span class='normal'>formularen virker og mailen sendes, men mail.php er omkring 1 MINUT !!! om </span><br /><span class='normal'>at afvikle. </span><br /><span class='normal'> </span><br /><span class='normal'>nogen der har en ide om hvad problemet kan v&#230;re ? </span><br /><span class='normal'> </span><br /><span class='normal'> - Tonny, <a href='http://www.jegergud.dk'>www.jegergud.dk</a> </span><br /><span class='normal'> </span><br /><span class='normal'></span><br /></p><hr /><ul class='newslist'><li class='newslist'><a href='/nyhedsgrupper/dk_edb_internet_webdesign_serverside_php/default.asp?messageid=%3Cba0au7%242ilq%241%40news%2Ecybercity%2Edk%3E' title='problem med mail()'>problem med mail()</a>&nbsp;<small class='newslist'>(15-05-03&nbsp;-&nbsp;tonny&nbsp;jørgensen)</small><ul class='relist'><li class='relist'><a href='/nyhedsgrupper/dk_edb_internet_webdesign_serverside_php/default.asp?messageid=%3Cspamdrop%2Bm31xz0upmf%2Efsf%40paven%2Ebunk%2Ecc%3E' title='Re: problem med mail()'>Re: problem med mail()</a>&nbsp;<small class='newslist'>(15-05-03&nbsp;-&nbsp;Jacob&nbsp;Bunk&nbsp;Nielsen)</small><ul class='relist'><li class='relist'><a href='/nyhedsgrupper/dk_edb_internet_webdesign_serverside_php/default.asp?messageid=%3Cba0hcb%242rnl%241%40news%2Ecybercity%2Edk%3E' title='Re: problem med mail()'>Re: problem med mail()</a>&nbsp;<small class='newslist'>(15-05-03&nbsp;-&nbsp;Tonny&nbsp;Jørgensen)</small><ul class='relist'><li class='relist'><a href='/nyhedsgrupper/dk_edb_internet_webdesign_serverside_php/default.asp?messageid=%3Cspamdrop%2Bm3wugst8qh%2Efsf%40paven%2Ebunk%2Ecc%3E' title='Re: problem med mail()'>Re: problem med mail()</a>&nbsp;<small class='newslist'>(15-05-03&nbsp;-&nbsp;Jacob&nbsp;Bunk&nbsp;Nielsen)</small><ul class='relist'><li